Because while you're cheering, your country is being stripped from the inside. Billionaires are getting richer at a historic rate, public services are being gutted, and the institutions that protected ordinary Americans for decades are being dismantled – by the very people you're defending. And somehow, the blame always lands on immigrants, on Europe, on ""elites."" Never on the man at the top who's been a billionaire his whole life.
